data.description: Welcome home to this stunning, beautifully maintained, single-level home in North Peoria's sought after Meadows community! SELLER IS OFFERING UP TO $10,000 IN SELLER CONCESSIONS. This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom open concept floor plan boasts beautiful tile floors throughout, bright & open kitchen/great room combo. Entertain effortlessly using the large slider in the main room, extending to the back patio. Large Master suite split from other bedrooms.  Entertain in your private backyard which includes luxury pavers, fireplace and artificial turf. Family friendly amenities and atmosphere is what makes The Meadows THE COMMUNITY you have been looking for, which offers: Heated pool, Jacuzzi, Outdoor Amphitheater, Pickle-ball Courts, playgrounds, and more. Make this dream home yours today
